replies.body:
Here comes the "I'm the victim" act. Please. Just get over it. Do the world a favor and get over the fact that you were trolled and got banned when you decided to return the favor.

I won't deny that everything you stated about what trolls do is frustrating, but like I said, I control what I do and what actions I take. I chose not to be toxic (most of the time). This is what it means to have self control. You clearly lack this.

I really am done with trying to help you move on buddy. :( I'm sorry your head is too thick for this. {{item:3151}}
